cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

The paper proposes the use of Convolutional Neural Networks for automatic brain tumor grading from MRI data, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of interpretability methodologies also suggests a focus on explainable AI (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves classification tasks, which could fall under the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves image processing and analysis, which could fall under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
